name: SB Defog - 5ml (Individual Retail Carton)
description:
Simply the best defog EVER!

Our flagship product will last you at least a full season of very active diving (approximately 100 dives).

The defog that you don't rinse!  Our defog doesn't have any harmful chemicals, is hypo-allergenic and will not cause eye or skin irritation.

You should consider ordering multiple to always make sure that you have some on hand.  We keep a bottle in our Dive Bag, our Mask Case and our BCD!

name: Display Pack
description:
This display will hold up to 12 5ml bottles of SB Scuba defog.  It's a perfect fit for point-of-sale applications measuring in at just 6"x2.5".

Make sure to purchase your stock of individual (non-retail carton) 5ml bottles of SB Scuba Defog to insure that you can replenish your inventory as customers purchase your product.

name: SB Defog - 5ml (Display Refills)
description: This is our product without any retail packaging.  You should select this to product to fill our retail store displays.

name: 60ml Instructor Bottle
description:
This version is perfect for the busy instructor or dive boat.  60ml is large enough to last through many hundreds of dives. 

This product is essential.  We carry a bottle on every trip, and it leads directly to retail sales of our 5ml product.
